eator-responds-to-racist-ass-taylor-swift-fans-looking-to-call-him-out-over-past-lyrics-3808812">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 粉丝因过去的歌词而指责他是“种族主义混蛋”，而造物主泰勒 (Tyler, The Creator) 的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
